Node.Notes: Assumes: [bring] Aaron [and] Nadab and Abihu, Eleazar and Ithamar, Aaron's sons.
Uncertain. Assumes: It shall be square, [it shall be] folded double. Probably means folded double to make a square bag.
A golden bell and a pomegranate is repeated, probably to suggest that they were to be placed alternately.
Holy to Yahweh is the inscription to be inscribed on the plate.
